Program: Last Word
Title: 30/10/2009
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b00nh0qv
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 1 Nov 2009
Matthew Bannister presents the obituary series. Marking the lives of actor and scriptwriter Norman Painting, voice of Phil Archer in The Archers, manager of Northern Ireland bus company during the Troubles Werner Heubeck, pediatric orthopedist Dr Ignacio Ponseti, international cricket upmire David Shepherd, and British silversmith William Phipps. Show less